<title>USA: Synopsys, Epic merger approved.</title>
<headline>Synopsys, Epic merger approved.</headline>
<dateline>MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif. 1997-02-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>Synopsys Inc and EPIC Design Technology Inc said shareholders of both companies approved their proposed merger.</p>
<p>Under terms of the merger, Synopsys will exchange 0.7485 of a share of its common stock for each share of EPIC common stock outstanding. Based on about 13.8 million EPIC shares outstanding, Synopsys will issue about 10.3 million shares, representing about 20.2 percent of Synopsys' outstanding shares.</p>
</text>
